Pick up the green apple from the trash can..

Put the apple on the counter under the knife.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Take the knife and slice the apple in half.
Turn around and face the sink.
Use the knife and slice the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Put the knife into the sink.
Take the center piece of the sliced apple out of the sink.
Turn around to face the counter.
Place the piece of sliced apple from the sink next to the apple on the counter.

Cut the apple in the sink into three slices
Put the knife into the sink
Grab one of the apple slices

Put the apple slice on the counter

Bend down and get the fruit out of the trash

Set the fruit down on the counter
Take the knife and cut the fruit in to slices
Take the knife to the kitchen sink
Slice the fruit that is in the sink
Set the knife down in the sink
Pick a slice of fruit from the kitchen sink
Turn around in the kitchen
Walk back to the counter
Set the fruit down on the counter
Turn left, walk across the room and turn right to face the trash can.
Pick up the green apple in the trash can.
Turn around and approach the counter to the right of the fridge.
Place the apple on the edge of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the apple into three pieces.
Turn around and approach the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple out of the sink.

Pick the apple up out of the black bin.

Put the apple on to the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into sections.

Cut the apple in the sink into sections.
Place the knife into the sink.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the dishwasher.
Place apple section to the right of other apple.
